Join the Kinomap community today! Integrated training programmes: The exercise bike is the perfect exercise bike equipped with 12 x automatic training programs from which you can choose between + 24 x manual resistance levels. Speed bike or simulate cross-country tours with variable incline and gradient resistance. Whisper-quiet movement: The 12 kg high performance flywheel and the low-noise chain drive system benefit from a secure braking system that allows you to quickly and easily stop your fitness bike. LCD display: Measure time, distance, calorie consumption and pulse rate on the multi-functional LCD display with backlight. Motivate yourself even more to achieve all your fitness goals. Home sports equipment from Bluefin Fitness. Low stress for joints, high training intensity: The Tour 5.0 exercise bike is the perfect indoor bike, it offers a cardio training of the highest class with low strain for your joints and many benefits for your health and fitness.
